We train. We motivate. We grow. Together.
Step up your game and join the family, so we can #GymsharkTrain together 🦈

#Gymsharktrain

#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Get ready to make that full body work with this powerful at-home HIIT workout from @mrandmrsmuscle 💪 
Tag a friend who you would duo this with!
#Gymsharktrain

Please only take part in the workout if you are medically and physically fit and have not been advised not to participate by a qualified medical professional. If your health or fitness changes adversely in any way before, during and/or after the workout please seek and follow medical advice without delay.

node.text:
@wozldn brings you a 🔥 full body workout to celebrate the last day of #Gymshark66! Expect 30 minutes of dynamic and energetic H.I.I.T exercises – you're defo going to need some water 🥵

Please only take part in the workout if you are medically and physically fit and have not been advised not to participate by a qualified medical professional. If your health or fitness changes adversely in any way before, during and/or after the workout please seek and follow medical advice without delay.

node.text:
Want to increase your flexibility? Then try this mobility flow routine by @jessicaolie 🙌
Click the link in our bio for more mobility workouts‼️ #Gymsharktrain

@nathan's bringing the heat to your house with this at-home core burner 🔥
Let's go:
1️⃣ Hip raise (4x10)
2️⃣ Decline mountain climber (4x20)
3️⃣ Crunches (4x10)
4️⃣ Step up plank (4x10)
5️⃣ Russian twist (4x20)
#Gymsharktrain

Effective at-home kettlebell leg workout with @tarasbody! 🙌
Focus on muscle contraction and think about squeezing your glutes 🍑 
1️⃣ Single leg deadlift (4x15)
2️⃣ Reverse lounge (4x15)
3️⃣ Sumo squat (4x15)
4️⃣ Sumo deadlift (4x15)
Tap save so you can try this in your own time ✔️
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Take care of those shoulders with the routine they deserve 💪
Follow along with @whitneyysimmons:
1️⃣ Leaning lateral raise (3x10)
2️⃣ Incline rainbow front raise (3x10)
3️⃣ Overhead tricep extensions (3x12)
4️⃣ Seesaw front press (3x12)
5️⃣ Superset: Cable tricep push-down to face pulls (3x10)
Swipe + save for some upper body inspiration ✅
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Get that workout in before your day begins! 👟 💥
Speedy cardio circuit with @_kylieross: 
1️⃣ Max sprint (20 sec on, 40 sec off, 4x rounds)
2️⃣ 1/2 burpees (x20)
3️⃣ Box jumps (x16)
4️⃣ Traveling jump squats (x16)
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Make sure you're doing these chest day exercises when you're next in the gym 🔥
@grosgui_fit's exercise routine:
1️⃣ Cross DB raise (4x12 each arm)
2️⃣ Bench press DB (4x10)
3️⃣ Pronate grip DB fly (4x12)
4️⃣ Incline bench press (4x10)
5️⃣ Decline push ups (4x12)
Hit save if you're ready to try this workout 🏋️
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
You need these exercises in your next leg day routine if you're looking to build that lower body 🙌
Follow along with @hxhails:
1️⃣ Sumo back squat
2️⃣ Narrow back squat with 3 abductors
3️⃣ Lunge with knee drives
4️⃣ Hip thrusts with abductors (10 abductors in last thrust)
Aim for no more than 15 reps per exercise ✅
#Gymsharktrain

🔥 Wide grip pull down (4x10-15 slow and controlled)
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Top pick lower body workout with @hannaoeberg 💥
Focus on form and prepare to make some serious gains 👇
1️⃣ BB sumo deadlift (7x12)
2️⃣ BB banded hip thrust (4x10)
3️⃣ BB landmine stiff deadlift (4x10)
4️⃣ Wide stance leg press (3x12-15)
5️⃣ Leg extensions SUPERSET with Heel elevated goblet squat (3x10)
6️⃣ Cable kickback (3x10)
#Gymsharktrain
